00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:06.919
<v Speaker 1>A state.

00:05:06.919 --> 00:05:08.199
<v Speaker 1>So how would you say that?

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:09.400
<v Speaker 1>I am free

00:05:10.860 --> 00:05:12.620
<v Speaker 2>Estoy libre.

00:05:12.620 --> 00:05:13.020
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:05:13.020 --> 00:05:14.139
<v Speaker 1>Estoy libre.

00:05:14.139 --> 00:05:17.660
<v Speaker 1>And libre does not change for masculine-feminine because it ends E.

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:21.020
