00:05:22.540 --> 00:05:23.500
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:32.919
<v Speaker 1>Now if you mean as a characteristic, as a characteristic of your personality, you are a free person, then you might say.

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:34.760
<v Speaker 2>Soy libre.

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:35.880
<v Speaker 1>Soy libre.

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:39.640
<v Speaker 1>You might also say I am a free person.

00:05:39.640 --> 00:05:42.280
<v Speaker 1>So person is persona.

00:05:42.280 --> 00:05:44.360
<v Speaker 1>And you could say I am a.

