00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:12.120
<v Speaker 1>In the sense of I am a busy person, and then you're sure it's perfect Spanish.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:14.760
<v Speaker 1>So how would you say I am a busy person?

00:08:15.699 --> 00:08:18.340
<v Speaker 2>Soy una persona occupada.

00:08:18.340 --> 00:08:18.740
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:08:18.740 --> 00:08:20.900
<v Speaker 1>Soy una persona occupada.

